result.name: Crystal Jade

reviews.text:
It's one of the very few places in the upscale shopping mall - Harbour City, for under HKD 100 per head. With that in mind, it's always packed.

Food is classical shanghai dishes with various dumplings and noodles. Quality is acceptable but nothing memorable.

Service is efficient but generally rushed.

It is a place for a quick meal or to sit down if you happen to be in Harbour City but I certainly would not recommend it as a destination.
Great food here! Stew beef noodle, pumpkin cake and fried rice were good

A specialist noodle and dumpling shop located within busy shopping mall Harbour City. Standard of food is fine but not top class. The noodle in spicy soup is nice as well as the dumplings. Be prepared to wait for 30 minutes at least during lunch hours.
Harbour City branch. Tasty dishes. A bit expensive for what they are...

Pro - relatively cheap, i mean you are in HK so.., fast, if you like to try asian food this is good start, dan dan ramen - peanut butter + spicy + instant noodle = love it!

Con - don’t expect good service, they through dishes at you, tea they give you when you seat - this is not free and unless you ask them to take away, they will charge you and it is expensive

reviews.text: ಠ╭╮ಠ

칠리새우에 상한 새우가 나왔습니다. 혼자 가서 샤오롱 바오, 마파 두부 등을 맛 본 후 칠리새우를 추가로 시켰는데 맛이 너무 없어  2개만 먹고 박스로 싸 왔는데 나중에 호탤에서 속이 역겨워져 박스는 열지도 않고 다 버렸네요.어제 귀국해서 이틀이 지났는데 오늘도 속이 안 좋습니다-.- 샤오롱 바오는 맛 있었고 추천합니다.
 I think the chilly shrimps I had went bad. Had only two pieces in the restaurant and later in the hotel  threw away everything in the box.

샤오롱바오 마파두부 볶음밥..다 맛나요. 바다보며 먹으니 더 좋구요 
하버시티 3층에 있어서
다니기도 수월했어요

這裡主打吃拉麵和沾麵，還有各式各樣特別的日式飲品，小食，定價亦很合理，份量亦很十足！小食點了三款，叉燒，炸雞和炒野菜。不過如果食量細的話，基本上點拉麵，加一個小食就很足夠了。炸雞一客有四件，炸得很脆之餘，雞肉亦好嫩！配合蛋黃醬或者特別的鹽，美味！
叉燒有兩塊，厚切亦很好軟熟。主食點了沾麵，湯底是中等稠身，不太稀亦不太濃。沾麵餸菜有蜆，叉燒條，還有溏心蛋！
另外的湯拉麵，湯底味道完全不一樣，一樣特別，而且很有蒜香味，同樣的嘅份量和配菜，麵底軟硬度煮得剛剛好，滿分！
홍콩 올 때마다 들려서 소룡포와 딴딴면 꼭 먹고갑니다. 이번 여행 중에는 2번이나 들러 먹었습니다. 차도 좋아서 여러번 마셨어요.
